# Rating 评分

用于收集打分或满意度反馈。支持半星精度、只读展示、自定义颜色、图标、尺寸与点击动画。

## 基础用法

### 半星评分

支持 `precision="0.5"` 半星评分。半星会从左侧填充。

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingBasicDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const score = ref(3.5)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="score" :precision="0.5" show-text />
  </template>
---
::

## 样式定制

通过 `filled-color`、`empty-color`、`hover-color`、`text-color`、`size` 与 `gap` 调整视觉样式。下面包含橙色、绿色只读与紫色紧凑三种外观。

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingStyleDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const score = ref(4)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating
      v-model="score"
      :size="28"
      :gap="6"
      :precision="0.5"
      filled-color="#f97316"
      empty-color="rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.34)"
      hover-color="#fb923c"
      text-color="var(--tx-color-warning)"
      show-text
    />
  </template>
---
::

## 自定义图标

`icon` 可以统一设置图标；也可以分别使用 `filled-icon`、`empty-icon`、`half-icon` 控制填充、空态与半星图标。支持内置图标、Iconify class 与 emoji，包括爱心、钻石和表情等。

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingIconDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const mood = ref(3)
  const hearts = ref(4.5)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="mood" icon="💎" :size="26" filled-color="#38bdf8" show-text />
    <TxRating
      v-model="hearts"
      :precision="0.5"
      :size="28"
      icon="i-carbon-favorite-filled"
      filled-color="#f43f5e"
      empty-color="rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.18)"
      show-text
    />
  </template>
---
::

## 点击动画

默认点击星级会触发更明显的 bounce + glow + ripple 动画；通过 `:animated="false"` 关闭。

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingAnimationDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const animated = ref(2)
  const still = ref(2)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="animated" :precision="0.5" show-text />
    <TxRating v-model="still" :animated="false" filled-color="#a78bfa" show-text />
  </template>
---
::

## 交互契约

Rating 会将星级组暴露为 radio group。`disabled` 与 `readonly` 都会阻止评分更新；`readonly` 是只展示模式，会移除星级按钮交互入口但保留评分展示。

## API（Lite）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: modelValue
    type: number
    default: '0'
    description: 当前评分
  - name: maxStars
    type: number
    default: '5'
    description: 星级数量
  - name: precision
    type: "number | 0.5"
    default: '1'
    description: 精度步进
  - name: showText
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 显示分数文本
  - name: disabled
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 禁用交互
  - name: readonly
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 只展示模式
  - name: icon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: '-'
    description: 统一设置评分图标
  - name: filledIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: 'star'
    description: 已填充图标
  - name: emptyIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: 'star'
    description: 空态图标
  - name: halfIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: '-'
    description: 半星图标；未设置时使用左侧裁切填充层
  - name: filledColor
    type: string
    default: '#fbbf24'
    description: 已填充颜色
  - name: emptyColor
    type: string
    default: '#d1d5db'
    description: 空态颜色
  - name: hoverColor
    type: string
    default: 'filledColor'
    description: 悬停颜色
  - name: textColor
    type: string
    default: '#6b7280'
    description: 分数文本颜色
  - name: size
    type: "number | string"
    default: '20px'
    description: 星级图标大小
  - name: gap
    type: "number | string"
    default: '2px'
    description: 星级间距
  - name: animated
    type: boolean
    default: 'true'
    description: 点击后是否播放 pop 动画
---
:::

